  2 write a user information management system
   user information can be stored in file, database, ldap or anything else.
   provide a web interface to customer to search user information by name and other field.
   the module they may need to study before writing:
  SimpleHttpServer

   If they have time, they can also try to implement a client to send request to the server and print returned value.
   The module they may be interested:
   httplib, urllib
